{
  "stem": "7546.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After we finished the barracks, which took, of course, a nice couple of weeks, I was going out to the factory, and I was building platforms for heavy machinery, which is, really, it's an hour to do it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You take four two-by-twos, you make a square, and then you pour cement in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the engineer that watched over us put in screws into the cement to stand up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it was already, with the measurement for the machinery that is going to go on this platform.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's what I did after we finish building the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in Braunschweig, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was two small villages.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was Braunschweig.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the war started getting closer and closer from the west, and from the north, and from the east, so-- and now, I'm rushing you through a little bit.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They closed Braunschweig, and they sent us to a town called Watenstedt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Watenstedt had a munition factory called the Hermann Goering Werke.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The factory belonged to Hermann Goering.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And over there, we were making straps for bullets for machine guns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And over there, we were just a short time, about three, four weeks, or maybe even less.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the English army started getting closer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From there, we went to Helmstedt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, yesterday, I remembered the exact-- Braunschweig was October.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Braunschweig was four months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we went to Watenstedt for about three to four weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was as far as January.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, then in Helmstedt and Bendorf together, we were about a month.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Then we were in a small camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were constantly on the go-- sometimes by foot, and sometimes by open car-- cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, for the munition factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
